{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudstag"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"A tag is a small element that shows short information like a label, keyword, or category.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It helps users quickly find, group, or understand content.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","platforms":[{"deprecated":false,"name":"iOS","unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"15.0"},{"deprecated":false,"name":"macOS","unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"15.0"},{"deprecated":false,"name":"tvOS","unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"16.0"},{"deprecated":false,"name":"visionOS","unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"1.0"},{"deprecated":false,"name":"watchOS","unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"11.0"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents7OUDSTagV","symbolKind":"struct","role":"symbol","title":"OUDSTag","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}]},"kind":"symbol","topicSections":[{"title":"Structures","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Status"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Structures"},{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/init(label:status:appearance:shape:size:hasLoader:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/init(loadingLabel:shape:size:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/body"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"title":"Enumerations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Appearance","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Shape","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Size"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Enumerations"},{"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/View-Implementations"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSTag"}]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Indicators"]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Appearances","text":"Appearances","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags have two appearances so as to highlight or not their content:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"emphasized"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag with a solid, high-contrast background. Used to draw strong attention to important","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"labels or categories. Emphasized tags stand out prominently against the interface and are ideal for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"primary or high-priority information.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"muted","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a subtle, light, or semi-transparent background. Used for secondary or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"less prominent information. Muted tags blend more with the background, providing a softer visual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"emphasis compared to emphasized tags."}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Status","anchor":"Status","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags have seven status depending on the context of the information they represent. Each state is designed"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to convey a specific meaning and ensure clarity in communication."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Neutral","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Default or inactive state. Used for standard labels, categories, or when no specific","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"status needs to be communicated.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Accent"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Used to draw attention to new features, recommendations, or content suggestions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Invites users to explore and engage with new offerings, creating an exciting and engaging experience."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Positive"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Indicates success, confirmation, or a positive status. Commonly used to highlight","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"completed actions or approved items.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Warning"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Signals caution or a potentially risky situation. Used to draw attention to items"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"requiring user awareness or intervention."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Negative"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Represents errors, critical issues, or urgent attention needed. Used to highlight"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"problems or failed actions."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Info"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Conveys informational messages or supplementary details. Used for neutral, helpful,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or contextual information."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Disabled"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Shows that the tag is inactive and cannot be interacted with. Appears faded or greyed out. This is not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"allowed when loader is activated."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Shape","text":"Shape","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags can have two shapes:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Rounded"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag with fully rounded corners, creating a pill-shaped appearance. Rounded","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"tags offer a softer and more approachable look, suitable for most modern interfaces.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Square"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with sharp, square corners. Squared tags provide a more formal, structured, or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"technical feel. They are often used in business contexts to label promotions, offers, or important notices."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Size","text":"Size","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags can have two sizes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Default","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": The standard tag size, suitable for most use cases and offering good readability."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Small"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A compact tag with reduced height and font size. Used when saving space is important or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when grouping elements visually."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Layout","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Layout"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There are four available layouts for tags:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text only","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that displays only text. Used for simple labels, categories, or keywords without additional visual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"elements."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text + Bullet"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a small indicator (dot) alongside the text. Used to show status, presence, or activity"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"next to the label."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"-","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text + Icon"}]},{"text":": A tag that includes an icon before the text. Used to visually reinforce the meaning of the tag,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"such as status, type, or action."}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Text + Loader","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that combines a loading spinner (or progress indicator) with text. Used to indicate that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a process or action related to the tag is in progress."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Text only with neutral status, for emphasized appearance with rounded shape in default size","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\",  status: .neutral(), appearance: .emphasized, shape: .rounded, size: .default)","    \/\/ Or also","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\")","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(leading: .bullet)","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with a custom decorative icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")))","    \/\/ If your layout is in RTL mode but your tag has an icon with another meaning because of bad orientation,","    \/\/ you can flip the icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"), flipIcon: true))","","    \/\/ Text with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(bullet: true))","","    \/\/ Tag with loader with rounded shape in small size","    OUDSTag(loadingLabel: \"Label\", shape: .rounded, size: .small)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/7565ce-tag","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Themes rendering","anchor":"Themes-rendering"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Orange","anchor":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_Orange"}]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Orange Business Tools","anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifie